message:
I'm using a third party library to convert a PDF to a Tiff. This library doesn't provide async methods. I've written a method that calls this library to convert a PDF in my MCV API web (HTTP) service. I then called this method using Task.Run which I now realize isn't correct. Is there any way to make this I/O bound method async?  

My code looks like:  
var success = await Task.Run(() => ConvertToTiff(filename));
